0search%3F%20I%20wouldn't!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-removes-chatgpt-feature-over-search-engine-privacy-concerns-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20raised%20some%20eyebrows%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20when%20people%20realized%20that%20certain%20chats%20were%20able%20to%20be%20found%20by%20Google%20search.%20Although%20people%20had%20checked%20a%20box%20to%20share%20the%20chats%20publicly%2C%20it%20seemed%20likely%20that%20not%20everyone%20understood%20what%20they%20were%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-competition-big-tech-meta-talent-windsurf-amazon-movie-deepmind-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20it%20would%20stop%20having%20shared%20chats%20be%20indexed%20by%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Meta's%20stand-alone%20MetaAI%20app%20also%20allows%20users%20to%20share%20their%20chats%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20allow%20Google%20to%20index%20them%2C%20meaning%20that%20they%20can%20show%20up%20in%20a%20search.%20I%20did%20a%20bunch%20of%20Google%20searches%20and%20found%20lots%20of%20MetaAI%20conversations%20in%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Meta%20AI%20app%2C%20launched%20this%20spring%2C%20lets%20people%20share%20chats%20to%20a%20%26quot%3BDiscover%26quot%3B%20feed.%20Google%20crawlers%20can%20%26quot%3Bindex%26quot%3B%20that%20feed%20and%20then%20serve%20up%20the%20results%20when%20people%20use%20Google%20search.%20So%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20if%20you%20do%20a%20site-specific%20search%20on%20Google%20for%20%26quot%3Bmeta.ai%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20keyword%20%26quot%3Bballoons%2C%26quot%3B%20you%20might%20come%20up%20with%20a%20chat%20someone%20had%20with%20the%20MetaAI%20bot%20about%20where%20to%20get%20the%20best%20birthday%20balloons%20%E2%80%94%20if%20that%20person%20tapped%20the%20button%20to%20allow%20the%20chat%20to%20be%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Business%20Insider%20reported%20in%20June%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-ai-chatbot-discover-feed-depressing-why-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20AI%20Discover%20feed%20had%20been%20full%20of%20examples%20of%20chats%20that%20seemed%20personal%20in%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20medical%20questions%2C%20specific%20career%20advice%2C%20relationship%20matters.%20Some%20contained%20identifying%20information%20like%20phone%20numbers%2C%20email%20addresses%2C%20or%20full%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20all%20of%20these%20people%20did%20click%20to%20share%2C%20based%20on%20the%20personal%20nature%20of%20some%20of%20the%20chats%2C%20I%20could%20only%20guess%20that%20people%20might%20have%20misunderstood%20what%20it%20meant%20to%20share%20the%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Business%20Insider%20wrote%20about%20this%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20the%20Meta%20AI%20app%20made%20some%20tweaks%20to%20warn%20users%20more%20clearly%20about%20how%20the%20Discover%20feed%20works.%20Now%2C%20when%20you%20choose%20to%20share%20a%20conversation%2C%20you%20get%20a%20pop-up%20with%20the%20warning%3A%20%26quot%3BConversations%20on%20feed%20are%20public%20so%20anyone%20can%20see%20them%20and%20engage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22730%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22meta%20ai%20app%20warning%20that%20feed%20is%20public%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688cfdde85e81483682f25cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22782%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Meta%20AI%20app%20warns%20you%20when%20before%20you%20share%20a%20post%20to%20the%20Discover%20feed.%3Cp%3EMeta%20AI%20%2F%20screenshot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20additional%20warning%20seems%20to%20be%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScrolling%20through%20the%20Discover%20feed%2C%20I%20now%20see%20mainly%20instances%20of%20people%20using%20it%20for%20image%20creation%