ll%20needs%20to%20be%20plugged%20into%20a%20power%20outlet.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221703%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20one%20of%20the%20Q990F's%20rear%20speakers%20resting%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688bd383f748d8c055f6acb5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221277%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Q990F's%20rear%20satellite%20speakers%20enable%20true%20surround%20sound%20playback.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you've%20bought%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-samsung-tvs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESamsung%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20the%20last%20few%20years%20(2022%20and%20newer)%2C%20you%20can%20connect%20the%20Q990F%20soundbar%20to%20your%20display%20wirelessly%20with%20full%20Dolby%20Atmos%20support.%20Otherwise%2C%20there's%20an%20eARC%20HDMI%20port%20on%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20soundbar%20for%20wired%20connectivity%20to%20any%20TV%20with%20HDMI.%20There's%20also%20an%20optical%20port%20for%20older%20TVs%2C%20but%20that%20kind%20of%20connection%20won't%20offer%20high-bandwidth%20sound%20quality%20or%20Dolby%20Atmos%20playback.%20I%20don't%20love%20that%20the%20ports%20are%20on%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20soundbar%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20a%20pain%20to%20access%2C%20but%20you%20shouldn't%20need%20to%20fiddle%20around%20with%20them%20too%20much%20after%20your%20initial%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20soundbar%20also%20has%20two%20handy%20HDMI%202.1%20passthrough%20ports.%20These%20connections%20can%20be%20used%20to%20pair%20a%20media%20device%2C%20like%20a%20streaming%20player%20or%20gaming%20console%2C%20to%20the%20soundbar%20and%20pass%20its%20video%20to%20your%20TV.%20Since%20they're%20version%202.1%2C%20these%20ports%20offer%20full%20support%20for%20sending%204K%2F120Hz%20signals%2C%20which%20is%20ideal%20if%20you%20want%20to%20pass%20vide