r.%20They%20each%20measure%20around%207.5%20inches%20tall%20and%205.5%20inches%20deep.%20Coated%20in%20the%20same%20dark%20gray%20color%2C%20they%20aren't%20particularly%20attractive%20decor%2C%20as%20I%20was%20told%20by%20my%20wife.%20They're%20straight%20out%20of%20the%20corporate%20collection%2C%20but%20they%20get%20the%20job%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221703%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20the%20integrated%20settings%20display%20on%20the%20front%20of%20the%20Samsung%20Q990F%20soundbar.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688bd37b3d5881a51c1e6557%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221277%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Q990F%20has%20a%20display%20for%20showing%20settings%20and%20other%20info%2C%20but%20its%20small%20size%20requires%20extensive%20text%20scrolling.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20system%20is%20designed%20well%20overall%2C%20I%20have%20one%20gripe%20with%20the%20soundbar's%20integrated%20text%20display%2C%20which%20is%20hidden%20behind%20its%20plastic%20grille.%20It's%20so%20small%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20scroll%20a%20bunch%20to%20display%20any%20settings%2C%20modes%2C%20or%20messages%20it%20tries%20to%20convey.%20This%20was%20also%20the%20case%20on%20older%20Q990%20models%2C%20but%20this%20choice%20is%20increasingly%20outdated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20while%20you%20can%20change%20settings%20on%20the%20soundbar%20using%20the%20remote%20control%2C%20I%20would%20recommend%20using%20the%20Samsung%20SmartThings%20mobile%20app%20instead.%20This%20app%20is%20used%20for%20all%20Samsung%20devices%20and%20is%20not%20purpose-built%20for%20home%20theater%20stuff%2C%20but%20it%20works%20well.%20My%20only%20complaint%20is%20that%20it%20doesn't%20display%20the%20current%20audio%20format%20that%20the%20soundbar%20is%20playing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20kind%20of%20information%20is%20useful%20if%20you%20want%20to%20confirm%20whether%20your%20system%20is%20properly%20receiving%20Dolby%20Atmos%20or%20other%20high-quality%20audio%20signals.%20As%20it%20stands%2C%20there's%20no%20way%20to%20see%20this%20in%20SmartThings.%20For%20people%20interested%2C%20this%20information%20is%20obtainable%20on%20the%20tiny%2C%20scrolling%20soundbar%20display%20if%20you%20press%20the%20%26quot%3Bi%26quot%3B%20button%20on%20the%20remote.%20But%20it%20should%20be%20in%20the%20app%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e94d542-2076-4f2e-884b-4a79985a927d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Sound%20quality%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESound%20quality%20is%20thoroughly%20impressive%20and%20immersive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223405%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20a%20Samsung%20Q990F%20resting%20on%20a%20media%20console%20underneath%20a%20TV%20mounted%20on%20the%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688bd4063d5881a51c1e6581%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222554%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Q990F%20delivers%20exceptional%20home%20theater%20performance.%20%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Samsung%20Q990F's%20main%20selling%20point%20is%20its%20high-end%20sound%20quality%20with%20an%20impressive%20756W%20of%20total%20power.%20And%20it%20doesn't%20disappoint.%20From%20the%20moment%20I%20turned%20the%20system%20on%20and%20pressed%20play%20on%20%26quot%3BDune%20II%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20was%20impressed.%20The%20subwoofer%20offered%20plenty%20of%20rumble%2C%20and%20the%20rear%20speakers%20instantly%20engulfed%20me%20in%20a%20sand-filled%20soundscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20watching%20movies%2C%20tires%20screeched%20with%20piercing%20clarity%2C%20and%20bullets%20fired%20with%20pointed%20sharpness.%20I%20cycled%20through%20the%20soundbar's%20different%20audio%20modes%2C%20such%20as%20Surround%2C%20Standard%2C%20and%20Adaptive%20Sound%2C%20to%20find%20the%20best%20option%20for%20my%20tastes.%20I%20was%20satisfied%20with%20each%20for%20different%20uses%2C%20but%20the%20nuances%20are%20there%20for%20those%20who%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDolby%20Atmos%20support%20is%20another%20big%20draw%20of%20the%20Q990F%2C%20as%20this%20feature%20allows%20the%20soundbar%20to%20simulate%20audio%20effects%20coming%20from%20above%20your%20head.%20You%20can%20learn%20more%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-dolby-atmos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDolby%20Atmos%20guide%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20the%20system%20performed%20beautifully.%20I%20ran%20through%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BReady%20Player%20One%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BTop%20Gun%3A%20Maverick%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20other%20titles%20with%20fun%20immersive%20scenes%2C%20and%20loved%20what%20the%20soundbar%20offered.%20All%20the%20drivers%20worked%20in%20conjunction%20to%20create%20a%20dome%20of%20audio%2C%20drawing%20me%20into%20the%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223405%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20the%20Samsung%20Q990F%20subwoofer%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20a%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688bd437f748d8c055f6ace8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222554%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20year's%20model%20has%20a%20more%20compact%20subwoofer%2C%20but%20it%20still%20offers%20deep%20low%20frequencies.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Q990F's%20subwoofer%20has%20been%20tweaked%20compared%20to%20previous%20models%2C%20as%20this%20new%20version%20has%20a%20more%20compact%2C%20sealed%20design%20that's%20built%20to%20reduce%20rattle.%20Though%20I%20couldn't%20directly%20compare%20it%20to%20the%20older%20ported%20subwoofer%2C%20I%20certainly%20like%20this%20new%20one's%20smaller%20size.%20Plus%2C%20it%20still%20packs%20a%20full-throttle%20punch.%20I%20didn't%20find%20the%20need%20to%20tweak%20any%20EQ%20settings%20when%20watching%20movies%2C%20but%20if%20you%20do%2C%20you%20can%20likely%20squeeze%20out%20even%20more%20oomph%20to%20shake%20your%20decor%20or%20annoy%20your%20neighbors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Q990F%20also%20supports%20Samsung's%20SpaceFit%20Sound%20Pro%20feature%2C%20which%20adapts%20the%20audio%20to%20your%20room's%20physical%20dimensions.%20There's%20no%20lengthy%20configuration%20process%20needed%2C%20and%20instead%2C%20you%20simply%20toggle%20it%20on%20and%20off%20in%20the%20SmartThings%20app.%20I%20noticed%20a%20slight%20difference%20in%20the%20audio%20performance%2C%20but%20not%20enough%20to%20be%20strict%20about%20turning%20it%20on.%20My%20living%20room%20is%20a%20rectangle%20without%20any%20odd%20reflections%2C%20so%20there's%20not%20much%20for%20it%20to%20adapt%20to.%20But%20to%20my%20ears%2C%20this%20feature%20did%20offer%20slightly%20tighter%20sound%20with%20less%20reverberation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20other%20audio%20tricks%20that%20you%20can%20perform%20using%20the%20SmartThings%20app.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20the%20advanced%20sound%20settings%2C%20you%20can%20activate%20%26quot%3BModerate%20Bass%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20turns%20the%20subwoofer%20off%20and%20lets%20the%20main%20soundbar%20handle%20all%20low-frequency%20duties.%20Apartment%20dwellers%20might%20find%20this%20useful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20%26quot%3BPrivate%20Rear%20Sound%26quot%3B%20function%20in%20the%20Surround%20Speaker%20Setup%20section.%20This%20option%20diverts%20all%20audio%20to%20the%20rear%20speakers%2C%20so%20sound%20playback%20is%20(theoretically)%20closer%20to%20the%20person%20or%20people%20sitting%20between%20the%20two%20rears.%20The%20sound%20quality%20wasn't%20anything%20special%20in%20this%20mode%2C%20but%20it%20does%20make%20for%20a%20neat%20way%20to%20watch%20TV%20after%20the%20kids%20have%20gone%20to%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20previous%20Q990%20soundbars%2C%20this%20model%20supports%20Samsung's%20Q-