ofit%20margins%2C%20solid%20revenue%20growth%2C%20and%20strong%20foothold%20in%20the%20design%20market.%20But%20the%20enormity%20of%20the%20pop%20reveals%20that%20Figma's%20record-breaking%20IPO%20day%20isn't%20really%20about%20the%20business%20itself%2C%20some%20experts%20told%20BI.%20Instead%2C%20it's%20a%20reflection%20of%20market%20frenzy%20for%20new%20tech%20IPOs%2C%20a%20demand%20that%20Figma's%20underwriters%20appear%20to%20have%20severely%20underestimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETanay%20Jaipuria%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Wing%20Venture%20Capital%2C%20said%20Figma's%20lead%20underwriters%20%E2%80%94%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20joined%20by%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20Allen%20%26amp%3B%20Co%2C%20and%20JP%20Morgan%20%E2%80%94%20seemingly%20misjudged%20the%20market's%20appetite%20for%20Figma's%20IPO%2C%20inadvertently%20cutting%20retail%20investors%20out%20of%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20stock's%20gain.%20%26quot%3BRetail%20feels%20very%20strongly%20when%20you%20see%20these%20big%20pops%20that%20the%20system's%20a%20little%20bit%20rigged%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Jaipuria%20argued%20that%2C%20as%20Figma%20trades%20at%20a%20multiple%20far%20above%20the%20normal%20range%20for%20enterprise%20software%20publics%2C%20the%20stock%20wasn't%20necessarily%20priced%20incorrectly%20based%20on%20the%20company's%20financials.%20It's%20the%20market's%20voracious%20appetite%20for%20tech%20listings%20like%20Figma%20driving%20up%20its%20price%20far%20beyond%20the%20norm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20fundamentals%20perspective%2C%20should%20Figma%20be%20at%20%2460%20billion%3F%20Probably%20not%2C%20right%3F%20But%20then%20you%20look%20at%20how%20CoreWeave%20and%20these%20other%20companies%20are%20trading%2C%20it's%20clear%20that%20there%20is%20just%20a%20lot%20of%20demand%20from%20retail%20and%20institutional%20investors%20for%20high-quality%20companies%20to%20go%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaipuria%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20critics%20say%20the%20banks%20behind%20the%20deal%20left%20billions%20on%20the%20table%20for%20Figma's%20investors%20and%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-bill-gurley-goldman-sachs-wall-street-revolutionized-ipo-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBenchmark%20general%20partner%20Bill%20Gurley%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%20in%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20IPO's%20pricing%20prevented%20Figma's%20selling%20shareholders%20from%20cashing%20out%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20additional%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20simple.%20They%20REFUSE%20to%20match%20supply%2Fdemand%20(that%20happened%20today).%20They%20brag%20about%20the%20mismatch%20%E2%80%94%20'30X%20oversubscribed.'%20The%20outcome%20is%20expected%20%26amp%3B%20fully%20intentional%2C%26quot%3B%20Gurley%20said%20in%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFigma%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20and%20JP%20Morgan%20declined%20to%20comment%20for%20this%20story.%20Morgan%20Stanley%20and%20Allen%20%26amp%3B%20Company%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffigma-ipo-party-wall-street-photos-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20went%20to%20Figma's%20IPO.%20It%20turned%20Wall%20Street%20into%20a%20literal%20block%20party%20with%20a%20DJ%20and%20free%20swag.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-got-rich-on-figma-ipo-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHere's%20who's%20getting%20rich%20from%20Figma's%20blockbuster%20IPO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffigma-ipo-donation-440-million-marin-community-foundation-evan-wallace-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20Figma%20IPO%20turned%20into%20a%20%24440%20million%20windfall%20for%20a%20nonprofit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5c73dd4-0e35-470b-8cef-c92efac09309%5C%22%3EFilling%20a%20void%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20been%20a%20dearth%20of%20tech%20public%20listings%20for%20the%20past%20three%20years.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20IPO%20window%20appears%20to%20have%20cracked%20open%2C%20with%20several%20VC-backed%20multibillion-dollar%20companies%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fchime-bank-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChime%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestors-executives-got-rich-hinge-health-ipo-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHinge%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%20testing%20the%20IPO%20waters%2C%20to%20mixed%20receptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20standout%20listings%20suggested%20retail%20investors%20were%20ready%20to%20send%20prices%20soaring%20in%20hot%20areas%2C%20however.%20Gil%20Luria%2C%20head%20of%20technology%20research%20at%20DA%20Davidson%2C%20pointed%20to%20crypto%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcircle-stock-price-usd-coin-crypto-crcl-ipo-genius-act-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECircle%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20AI%20cloud-computing%20player%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoreweave-weak-ipo-ai-skepticism-nvidia-gpu-neocloud-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECoreWeave%3C%2Fa%3E's%20IPOs%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Both%20saw%20explosive%20stock%20surges%20after%20their%20debuts%2C%20despite%2C%20in%20his%20assessment%2C%20posting%20far%20weaker%20business%20fundamentals%20than%20Figma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20behavior%20tells%20us%20more%20about%20the%20market%20than%20it%20does%20about%20Figma%2C%26quot%3B%20Luria%20said%20of%20Figma's%20IPO%20pop.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20learned%20from%20CoreWeave%20and%20Circle%20was%20that%20there's%20such%20an%20appetite%20for%20new%20issuances%20that%20investors%20are%20willing%20to%20look%20past%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20business%20being%20issued.%20Figma%20is%20benefiting%20from%20that.%20The%20difference%20between%20Figma%2C%20CoreWeave%2C%20and%20Circle%20is%20that%20Figma%20is%20a%20real%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Erickson%2C%20an%20adjunct%20professor%20at%20Columbia%20Business%20School%20and%20a%20former%20investment%20banker%20at%20Barclays%20and%20Lehman%20Brothers%2C%20noted%20that%20Figma's%20underwriters%20set%20the%20company's%20IPO%20valuation%20at%20close%20to%2020%20times%20its%20sales.%20That's%20already%20far%20above%20the%20typical%20multiple%20for%20public%20software%20companies%2C%20which%20traded%20at%20a%20median%20of%20six%20times%20their%20sales%20in%20July%2C%20per%20Aventis%20Advisors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFigma's%20underwriters%20also%20raised%20its%20IPO%20pricing%20multiple%20times%20after%20confronting%20surging%20demand%20during%20the%20company's%20roadshow.%20They%20almost%20certainly%20expected%20a%20pop%20at%20its%20IPO%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bthey%20clearly%20didn't%20think%20it%20was%20going%20to%20trade%20at%20%2485%2C%26quot%3B%20Erickson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20people%20looking%20to%20play%20the%20next%20hot%20IPO%2C%20and%20that%20was%20Figma%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGurley%20and%20other%20critics%20argued%20that%20the%20initial%20pricing%20hurt%20Figma%20investors%20and%20employees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffigma-ipo-donation-440-million-marin-community-foundation-evan-wallace-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewho%20sold%20shares%20in%20the%20IPO%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20it's%20true%20that%20they%20could've%20made%20more%20money%20had%20Figma's%20underwriters%20better%20approximated%20the%20opening%20share%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20Figma's%20significant%20investors%20didn't%20sell%20large%20amounts%20of%20shares%20at%20its%20IPO%20relative%20to%20their%20total%20holdings%2C%20though.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-got-rich-on-figma-i