w-broken-our-education-system-is-economist-says-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprevent%20students%20from%20using%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20encouraging%20it%20or%20teaching%20it.%20This%20is%20partly%20because%20AI%20use%20in%20school%20is%20considered%20cheating.%20There%20is%20also%20concern%20that%20using%20AI%20can%20cause%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bbrain%20rot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelsky%20thinks%20about%20it%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20ultimately%20a%20tool%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20at%20one%20point%20comparing%20it%20to%20a%20calculator.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20matters%20most%20in%20an%20education%20space%20is%20how%20that%20tool%20is%20used.%20If%20students%20use%20AI%20as%20an%20answer%20machine%2C%20they%20are%20not%20going%20to%20learn.%20And%20so%20part%20of%20our%20journey%20here%20is%20to%20help%20students%20and%20educators%20use%20AI%20in%20ways%20that%20will%20expand%20critical%20thinking%20and%20expand%20creativity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bcore%20literacy%26quot%3B%20students%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eshould%20develop%2C%20she%20said%2C%20is%20coding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20with%20vibe%20coding%20and%20now%20that%20there%20are%20all%20sorts%20of%20tools%20that%20make%20coding%20easier%2C%20I%20think%20we're%20going%20to%20get%20to%20a%20place%20where%20every%20student%20should%20not%20only%20learn%20how%20to%20use%20AI%20generally%2C%20but%20they%20should%20learn%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20create%20images%2C%20to%20create%20applications%2C%20to%20write%20code%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVibe%20coding%20is%20the%20process%20of%20prompting%20AI%20in%20natural%20language%20to%20write%20code%20for%20whatever%20you%20want.%20It's%20been%20widely%20embraced%2C%20but%20most%20avoid%20using%20it%20for%20core%20technology%20since%20AI%20code%20is%20prone%20to%20errors.%20Anyone%20vibe%20coding%20would%20need%20some%20level%20of%20coding%20knowledge%2C%20or%20know%20someone%20