ressed%20oils%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20running%20a%20large-scale%20venture%20was%20not%20easy.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20traders%20felt%20threatened%20by%20our%20model.%20They%20were%20used%20to%20controlling%20the%20market%2C%20but%20we%20believed%20in%20the%20power%20of%20direct%20trade%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20says.%20Despite%20their%20venture%20causing%20some%20tension%20in%20the%20local%20markets%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20pressed%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20soon%20the%20young%20entrepreneur%20realised%20that%20offering%20higher%20incentives%20to%20farmers%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20to%20sustain%20long-term%20growth.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20business%20became%20increasingly%20seasonal%2C%20with%20supply%20chain%20challenges%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20maintain%20consistent%20operations.%20So%2C%20we%20had%20to%20stop%20our%20operations%20in%20Uttarakhand%20and%20come%20up%20with%20a%20better%20approach%20to%20expand%20our%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20cold-pressed%20oil%20brand%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20second%20COVID-19%20wave%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20noticed%20an%20increasing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328846%2Fsibi-manivannan-runs-gramiya-cold-pressed-oils-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemand%20for%20cold-pressed%20oils%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20insight%20led%20them%20to%20pivot%20their%20business%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202022%2C%20the%20Heart%20in%20Hills%20team%20ventured%20into%20the%20cold-pressed%20oil%20market%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20Foreka%20in%20Rajasthan.%20This%20expansion%20was%20made%20possible%20by%20the%20support%20Satyam%20received%20in%20November%202020%2C%20when%20he%20was%20awarded%20a%20prestigious%20fellowship%20from%20The%20Buddha%20Institute%2C%20founded%20by%20Ved%20Arya%2C