india.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20project%20involved%20clearing%2012%20truckloads%20of%20waste%20and%20recycling%201%2C600%20kilograms%20of%20plastic%20into%20benches.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477273%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20project%20involved%20clearing%2012%20truckloads%20of%20waste%20and%20recycling%201%2C600%20kilograms%20of%20plastic%20into%20benches.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20hard%20road%20to%20restoring%2010%20acres%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20verifying%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20spanning%2010%20acres%20filled%20with%20municipal%20and%20industrial%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20Vikrant%20mobilised%20efforts%20through%20his%20non-profit%2C%20SAFE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20this%20herculean%20challenge%2C%20he%20first%20secured%20the%20much-needed%20No%20Objection%20Certificate%20from%20the%20Greater%20Noida%20Industrial%20Development%20Authority%20to%20transform%20the%20site.%20His%20strategy%20was%20clear%3A%20involve%20community%20volunteers%2C%20