anted%20saplings%20thrived%2C%20breathing%20life%20into%20the%20once-neglected%20patch%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-2_11zon-1753705295.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20community%20support%2C%20SAFE%20levelled%20the%20land%20to%20fix%20the%20illegal%20mining%20pits%20and%20prepare%20the%20site%20for%20tree%20planting.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-2_11zon-1753705295.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-2_11zon-1753705295-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-2_11zon-1753705295-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-2_11zon-1753705295-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-2_11zon-1753705295-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477276%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20community%20support%2C%20SAFE%20levelled%20the%20land%20to%20fix%20the%20illegal%20mining%20pits%20and%20prepare%20the%20site%20for%20tree%20planting.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20locals%20become%20guardians%20of%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20the%20project%20didn%E2%80%99t%20rest%20on%20Vikrant%20alone.%20He%20is%20quick%20to%20credit%20the%20community%20for%20sparking%20and%20sus