0approach%20along%20with%20Rainmatter%20Foundation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Devjit%20Mittra%2C%20Executive%20Director%20of%20Socratus%20Foundation%20in%20India%2C%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20look%20for%20anchors%20in%20each%20place%20%E2%80%94%20people%20already%20trusted%20by%20the%20community%2C%20like%20Nirakar%20or%20Madhusmit%20%E2%80%94%20and%20through%20them%2C%20we%20start%20real%20conversations.%20People%20begin%20talking%20about%20restoring%20ecosystems%20and%20reviving%20livelihoods.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20goal%20is%20clear%3A%20help%20people%20move%20from%20feeling%20powerless%20to%20feeling%20capable%20and%20in%20control.%20To%20make%20this%20vision%20real%2C%20Socratus%20created%20a%20coalition%20of%20civil%20society%20organisations%20active%20in%20India%20and%20Odisha.%20Their%20collaborators%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Bakul%20Foundation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20volunteer-driven%20movement%20in%20Odisha%20enabling%20public%20initiatives%20like%20free%20libraries%20and%20art%20programmes.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESambad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20major%20Odia%20news%20outlet.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoonj%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20humanitarian%20organisation%20working%20on%20disaster%20relief%20and%20rural%20development.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESELCO%20Foundation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20develops%20decentralised%20renewable%20energy-based%20solutions.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20new%20way%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20weather%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Socratus%20began%20looking%20for%20a%20place%20to%20test%20its%20ideas%2C%20Odisha%20felt%20like%20the%20obvious%20choice.%20The%20state%20lives%20under%20the%20constant%20threat%20of%20cyclones%20and%20floods.%20Its%20landscapes%20%E2%80%94%20from%20dense%20forests%20